Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Hand MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Ganglion' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Flexor tendons' radio button is enabled
And 'Extensor tendons' radio button is enabled

And 'Size' input field is enabled
And 'Intratendinous' radio button is enabled
And 'Peritendinous' radio button is enabled

And 'Signal characteristics T1w' slidebar is enabled
And 'Signal characteristics T2w' slidebar is enabled

And 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Septated' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Flexor tendons' radio button
Then 'Details flexor tendons' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Extensor  tendons' radio button
Then 'Details extensor tendons' dropdown menu is enabled

When I enter any value from 1 to 50 in 'Size' input field
Then '2nd plane' input field is enabled

When I enter any value from 1 to 50 in '2nd plane' input field
Then '3rd plane' input field is enabled
